title: McGee Sees Resilient Consumer, Inflation Concerns
itunes:title: McGee Sees Resilient Consumer, Inflation Concerns
description:
Tom McGee, President of ICSC, discusses strong consumer spending and whether inflation could ultimately impact the sector.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
